QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when logging -> 'TargetBucket' is null then 'alarm'
    else 'ok'
  end as status,
  case
    when logging -> 'TargetBucket' is null then title || ' logging disabled.'
    else title || ' logging enabled.'
  end as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_s3_bucket;
